-- Poland to Cut 10% of Government Jobs, Limit Workforce to Reduce Spending
-- B y   M o n i k a   R o z l a l
-- 2010-10-26T17:44:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/poland-to-cut-10-of-government-jobs-limit-workforce-to-reduce-spending.html
Poland plans to cut 10 percent of
its government jobs and will maintain a “limited level of
workforce” through 2013 to reduce spending, the cabinet said in
an e-mail today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Monika Rozlal in Warsaw at 
